s 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.30\">3, 4, 6, 7, 8</acronym> turns and doing <acronym class=\"talent-variable\" title=\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5,<br>talent mastery 1.30\">75%, 90%, 101%, 111%, 119%</acronym> damage.</p><p>Daze chance increases with talent level.</p>","mode":"activated","source_code":["data/talents/spells/golem.lua",211],"radius":2,"stamina":5,"cooldown":15,"type":["golem/fighting",4],"require":["Level 12, Str 36","Level 13, Str 38","Level 14, Str 40","Level 15, Str 42","Level 16, Str 44"],"name":"Pound"}],"name":"fighting","description":"Golem melee capacity."},{"points":1,"__ATOMIC":true,"type":"golem/golem","talents":[{"points":1,"no_unlearn_last":true,"id":"T_GOLEM_DESTRUCT","image":"golem_destruct.png","range":"0.0","radius":4,"info_text":"<p>The golem self-destructs, destroying itself and generating a blast of fire in a radius of 4, doing <acronym class=\"stat-variable\" title=\"Values for<br>character level 1, 10, 25, 40, 50\">60, 150, 300, 450, 550</acronym> fire damage.</p><p>This spell is only usable when the golem's master is dead.</p>","short_name":"GOLEM_DESTRUCT","mode":"activated","use_speed":"Standard","source_code":["data/talents/spells/golem.lua",480],"type":["golem/golem",1],"name":"Self-destruction"},{"points":6,"no_unlearn_last":true,"id":"T_GOLEM_ARMOUR","mode":"passive","source_code":["data/talents/spells/golem.lua",511],"info_text":"<p>The golem automatically reconfigures heavy mail and massive armours designed for living creatures to protect its own vital areas.</p><p><acronym class=\"talent-variable\" title=\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5\">Decreases, Decreases, Increases, Increases, Increases</acronym> armour value by <acronym class=\"talent-variable\" title=\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5\">-2, -1, 0, 1, 2,</acronym> armour hardiness by <acronym class=\"talent-variable\" title=\"Values for<br>talent levels 1-5\">-10%, -5%, 0%, 5%, 10%,</acronym> and provides <acronym class=\"talent-variable\" title=\"Values for<br>ta